ttps://www.gov.uk/government/ministers/minister-of-state-minister-for-equalities\">Minister for Equalities</a>) in the <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/the-equality-hub\">Equality Hub</a> between 14 February 2020 and July 2022.</p>\n\n<p>She was previously Exchequer Secretary to the Treasury from 13 February 2020 to 15 September 2021 and Parliamentary Under Secretary of State at the Department for Education from 27 July 2019 to 13 February 2020.</p>\n\n<p>Image credit: UK Parliament. Used under <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/\">Creative Commons</a></p>\n","image":{"alt_text":"The Rt Hon Kemi Badenoch MP","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/623861938fa8f540f6c231e4/s465_Kemi_gov.uk.png"}},"document_type":"person","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-07-18T09:49:52Z","schema_name":"person","title":"The Rt Hon Kemi Badenoch MP","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/kemi-badenoch","withdrawn":false}],"role":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/ministers/secretary-of-state--2","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/ministers/secretary-of-state--2","base_path":"/government/ministers/secretary-of-state--2","content_id":"5cb74a2c-7e9f-444a-8347-d944cc05b606","details":{"body":"<p>The Secretary of State has overall responsibility for the Department for Business and Trade. Responsibilities include:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>overall responsibility for delivery and strategy</li>\n  <li>cross-government business engagement</li>\n  <li>public appointments</li>\n  <li>FTA negotiations, mandates, and decisions</li>\n  <li>WTO, G7, and G20 ministerial meetings</li>\n  <li>overseas network​</li>\n</ul>\n","role_payment_type":null,"seniority":17,"whip_organisation":{}},"document_type":"ministerial_role","links":{"ordered_parent_organisations":[{"analytics_identifier":"D1382","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/department-for-business-and-trade","api_url":"https: